msgid "Appendix E: QGIS Application Network Connections"
msgstr "Dodatak E: Mrežne veze QGIS aplikacije"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/appendices/qgis_desktop_network_connections.rst:5
msgid ""
"This is a list of the pre-configured/automated network connections that QGIS"
" makes. Some of the connections are user initiated because they require an "
"action from the user before they take place, others happen automatically."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je lista unapred konfigurisanih/automatizovanih mrežnih veza koje QGIS "
"uspostavlja. Neke veze pokreće korisnik jer zahtevaju radnju korisnika pre "
"nego što se ostvare, a druge se dešavaju automatski."

